# ============================================================
# TRADE CORE RUNTIME
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: runtime
domain: trade
scope: trade.core
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for trade.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers trade visibility,
proposal state,
approval state,
active exchange state,
dispute state,
closure state,
and bounded failure rendering.

## validation_rules
- trade identity must resolve
- parties must resolve
- exchange scope must resolve
- approval scope must be valid
- policy scope must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid trade parties
- invalid exchange scope
- invalid approval path
- invalid closure path
- safe runtime fallback

## observability
Runtime must emit enough signals
to distinguish proposal,
approval,
active exchange,
dispute,
closure,
and failure state.

## review_checklist
- trade states are explicit
- approval-aware runtime is explicit
- failure handling is explicit
